Build an Express app to display a list of people, each with their own page containing more information about them. This will help illustrate the need for templates, because it will become increasingly tedious to create a page for each individual person.
Getting Started

Open up a terminal, create a new folder for the People List project, and cd into it
Run npm init, taking all of the defaults other than setting app.js for the entry point
Install Express with npm install express --save
Create a new file in the People List project folder named home.html
